                                        <break/>Action 3: Capacity-building budget for ECRs
                                        <break/>
                                        <break/>
                                        <bold>Involvement in decision-making</bold>
                                        <break/>Action 4: ECR inclusion in decision-making and leadership roles
                                        <break/>
                                        <break/>
                                        <bold>Career continuity</bold>
                                        <break/>Action 5: Bridge careers after project completion
                                        <break/>Action 6: ECR network and community platform</td>
                                </tr>
